Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.72,0:24:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Baha baha baha soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.26,0:24:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Los espero la próxima semana.
